H4 delimiter? procedure

The K{delimiter?} helper procedure recognizes delimiter characters between value
representations.

CB(
proc ::constcl::delimiter? {c} {
  if {$c in {( ) ; \" ' ` | [ ] \{ \}}} {
    return #t
  } else {
    return #f
  }
}
CB)

